      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is an absolute dream and has been meticulously cared for\u2014it\u2019s in showroom condition and literally looks like it just rolled off the lot! No scratches, no dings, and it drives like a dream. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
