      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s specimen, maintained with an obsessive attention to detail that is evident from every angle. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state, featuring supple leather that retains its factory scent and pristine surfaces free of any wear or sun damage. Mechanically, it is flawless; the engine runs with whisper-quiet precision, and the gear transitions are seamless. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
